{"word":"H3857 - לָהַט - lâhaṭ - law-hat' - Burn","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">לָהַט</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>lâhaṭ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>law-hat'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Burn"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தீயை இறை, ஜுவாலை, எரித்துப்போடு, எரி, வேகப்பண்ணு, கொளுத்து, சுட்டெரி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to burn, to blaze, to scorch, to kindle, to blaze up, to flame"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) blazing (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to scorch, to burn, to blaze"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>lick</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>blaze: - </i>burn (up), set on fire, flaming, kindle."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3857 - לָהַט - lâhaṭ - law-hat'/3857\">H3857</a>, <a href=\"#/H3858 - לַהַט - lahaṭ - lah'-hat/3858\">H3858</a>"}]}